<h2 id="hd_id3146986">Show input help when cell is selected</h2>
<paragraph role="paragraph" id="par_id3153363"><ahelp hid="modules/scalc/ui/validationhelptabpage/tsbhelp">Displays the message that you enter in the <emph>Contents</emph> box when the cell or cell range is selected in the sheet.</ahelp></paragraph>
